<item>
            <title>[LU-11817] LNet: timing statistics</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11817</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add statistics to measure the average/maximum time spent in the LNet/LNDs for the following cases:&lt;br/&gt;
1. Average/maximum time for receiving an LNet ACK/REPLY&lt;br/&gt;
2. Average/maximum time messages are queued on the LND outgoing queues&lt;br/&gt;
3. Average/maximum time LND transmits remain active (IE awaiting completion, either via response or a completion event).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Add ability to extract these values from lnetctl.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
